13. What are the regulations and standards governing the electronic overload relay market?
The electronic overload relay market is regulated by standards such as IEC 60947, UL 508, and NEMA standards, among others.

14. What are the factors influencing the pricing of electronic overload relays?
The factors influencing the pricing of electronic overload relays include the type of relay, power rating, brand reputation, and additional features such as communication interfaces and diagnostic capabilities.

